title: Rock Sample
description: A rough, irregularly shaped rock with a dark greenish hue and visible texture. The surface appears to have some striations and variations in color, suggesting mineral composition.

title: Ancient Engraved Stone
description: A piece of stone with visible engravings or carvings on its surface. The stone has a rough texture and a reddish-brown color, suggesting it may be of natural origin. The engravings appear to be linear and abstract, possibly indicating some form of ancient writing or artistic expression.

title: Lava Flow
description: The image depicts a close-up view of a lava flow, showcasing the textured surface of solidified lava with dark, rocky areas and bright red-orange sections indicating areas of heat or molten lava beneath the surface.

title: Volcanic Landscape
description: An illustration depicting a volcanic landscape. On the right, a volcano is shown erupting, with lava flowing down its sides and smoke billowing from the top. To the left, there is a serene beach scene with golden sand and a calm blue ocean, along with green hills and small islands in the distance. The image contrasts the violent nature of the volcano with the peacefulness of the beach.

title: Piece of Petrified Wood
description: A piece of petrified wood, showcasing a cylindrical shape with a rough, textured surface. The wood appears to have a light color with some orange and brown hues, indicating the mineralization process that has turned it into stone.
